{"0":"It looks like the configuration change did not take effect, as the execution host is still not allowing `node` requests. This might be due to a misconfiguration or a limitation in the current environment.\n\nGiven the constraints, let's try a simpler approach to generate the screenshot without relying on the `playwright` command directly. Instead, we can use a headless browser to render the page and capture the screenshot.\n\nWe'll use the `playwright` library to launch a headless browser and capture the screenshot. Here’s how we can do it:\n\n1. Install `playwright` if not already installed.\n2. Launch a headless browser.\n3. Navigate to the generated HTML page.\n4. Capture the screenshot.\n\nLet's proceed with this plan:\n\n1. Install `playwright`:\n\n```sh\npip install playwright\n```\n\n2. Use `playwright` to capture the screenshot:\n\n```sh\nplaywright launch --headless --no-sandbox \\\n  --viewport-size=1920,1080 \\\n  --ignore-ssl-errors=yes \\\n  --disable-gpu \\\n  --disable-dev-shm-usage \\\n  --remote-debugging-port=9222 \\\n  --window-size=1920,1080 \\\n  --user-agent=\"Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/83.0.4103.116 Safari/537.36\" \\\n  --screenshot /tmp_workspace/results/screenshot.png \\\n  file:///tmp_workspace/results/index.html\n```\n\nLet's execute these steps:\n\n1. Install `playwright`:\n```sh\npip install playwright\n```\n\n2. Capture the screenshot:\n```sh\nplaywright launch --headless --no-sandbox \\\n  --viewport-size=1920,1080 \\\n  --ignore-ssl-errors=yes \\\n  --disable-gpu \\\n  --disable-dev-shm-usage \\\n  --remote-debugging-port=9222 \\\n  --window-size=1920,1080 \\\n  --user-agent=\"Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/83.0.4103.116 Safari/537.36\" \\\n  --screenshot /tmp_workspace/results/screenshot.png \\\n  file:///tmp_workspace/results/index.html\n```\n\nLet's run these commands in sequence:\n\n```sh\npip install playwr